stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Lobby: Game Created
    
    Lobby --> Starting: Host starts game<br/>(2+ players)
    Lobby --> [*]: Game deleted<br/>(host cancels)
    
    Starting --> InProgress: Cards dealt<br/>Turn assigned
    Starting --> Lobby: Start failed<br/>(error occurred)
    
    InProgress --> InProgress: Card played<br/>Card drawn<br/>Turn advanced
    InProgress --> Paused: Host pauses<br/>Player disconnects
    InProgress --> RoundEnded: Player empties hand
    
    Paused --> InProgress: Host resumes<br/>Player reconnects
    Paused --> [*]: Game abandoned<br/>(timeout)
    
    RoundEnded --> InProgress: New round started<br/>(cards redealt)
    RoundEnded --> GameEnded: Final round complete<br/>Winner declared
    RoundEnded --> RoundEnded: Rule being proposed<br/>(winner's turn)
    
    GameEnded --> [*]: Game archived
    
    note right of Lobby
        Players can:
        - Join game
        - Leave game
        - Mark ready
        - Chat
    end note
    
    note right of InProgress
        Players can:
        - Play cards
        - Draw cards
        - Chat
        - View game state
        
        System:
        - Enforces rules
        - Applies penalties
        - Advances turns
    end note
    
    note right of RoundEnded
        Winner can:
        - Propose new rule
        - Decline to propose
        
        System waits for:
        - Rule proposal
        - Rule compilation
        - Rule approval
    end note
    
    note right of Paused
        Reasons for pause:
        - Player disconnected
        - Host paused
        - Technical issue
        
        Auto-resume when:
        - Player reconnects
        - Host resumes
        - Issue resolved
    end note